{"total": "===========================================================================\n                          \uac15\ub3c4\uc124\uacc4\ubc95(USD)\uc5d0 \uc758\ud55c \ud728\ubaa8\uba58\ud2b8 \uac80\ud1a0                           \n===========================================================================\n\n1) \ub2e8\uba74\uc81c\uc6d0 \ubc0f \uc124\uacc4\uac00\uc815\n   fck = 35.0 MPa, fy = 400.0 MPa, \u00d8f = 0.85, \u00d8v = 0.75, Es = 200000 MPa\n   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n   |  B(mm)   |  H(mm)   |  d(mm)   |  \ud53c\ubcf5(mm)  |   Mu(N.mm)   |   Vu(N)    |  Ms(N.mm)  |\n   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n   |   400    |   600    |  520.0   |   80.0   |  100000000   |   50000    |  60000000  |\n   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n2) \ucf58\ud06c\ub9ac\ud2b8 \uc7ac\ub8cc\uc0c1\uc218\n   \u03b21   : \ub4f1\uac00 \uc0ac\uac01\ud615 \uc751\ub825 \ube14\ub85d\uc758 \uae4a\uc774\uacc4\uc218           = 0.801\n\n3) \uac15\ub3c4\uac10\uc18c\uacc4\uc218(\u00d8) \uc0b0\uc815\n   T = As x fy = 2026.800 x 400.000 = 810720.0 N\n   C = 0.85 x fck x a x b = 0.85 x 35.000 x a x 400.000 = 11900.0 x a\n   T = C \uc774\ubbc0\ub85c, a = 68.128 mm, c = a / \u03b21 = 68.128 / 0.801 = 85.053 mm\n   \u03b5y = fy / Es = 400.0 / 200000 = 0.00200\n   \u03b5t = 0.00300 x (dt - c) / c = 0.00300 x (520.000 - 85.053) / 85.053 = 0.01534\n   \u03b5t \u2265 0.0050 \uc774\ubbc0\ub85c \uc778\uc7a5\uc9c0\ubc30\ub2e8\uba74\uc774\uba70, \u00d8 = 0.85 \ub97c \uc801\uc6a9\ud55c\ub2e4\n\n4) \ud544\uc694\ucca0\uadfc\ub7c9 \uc0b0\uc815\n   Mu / \u00d8f = As x fy x (d - a / 2)              ---------------- \u2460\n   a = As x fy / (0.85 x fck x b)               ---------------- \u2461\n   \uc2dd\u2461\ub97c \uc2dd\u2460\uc5d0 \ub300\uc785\ud558\uc5ec \uc774\ucc28\ubc29\uc815\uc2dd\uc73c\ub85c As\ub97c \uad6c\ud55c\ub2e4\n           fy\u00b2                                Mu\n   ------------------ As\u00b2 - fy x d x As + ------ = 0 ,  Asreq = 576.347 mm\u00b2\n    2 x 0.85 x fck x b                         \u00d8f\n\n5) \uc0ac\uc6a9\ucca0\uadfc\ub7c9 : Asuse = 2026.8 mm\u00b2, \ucca0\uadfc\ub3c4\uc2ec : do = 520.0mm, [ \uc0ac\uc6a9\uc728 = 3.517 ]\n   1\ub2e8 : D 25 - 4.0 EA (= 2026.8 mm\u00b2, do1 = 80.0 mm)\n   2\ub2e8 : D 0 - 0 EA (= 0.0 mm\u00b2, do2 = 0.0 mm)\n   3\ub2e8 : D 0 - 0 EA (= 0.0 mm\u00b2, do3 = 0.0 mm)\n\n6) \ucca0\uadfc\ube44 \uac80\ud1a0\n   \u03c1min : 1.4 / fy          = 0.003500\n          0.25 x \u221afck / fy  = 0.003698, \u03c1min = 0.003698 \uc801\uc6a9\n   \u03c1max = 0.75 x \u03c1b = 0.75 x (0.85 x \u03b21 x fck / fy) x (6000 / (6000 + fy)) = 0.041888\n   \u03c1use = As / ( b x d ) = 0.009744\n   \u03c1max \u2265 \u03c1use \u2265 \u03c1min --> \ucd5c\uc18c\ucca0\uadfc\ube44, \ucd5c\ub300\ucca0\uadfc\ube44 \ub9cc\uc871   \u2234 O.K\n\n7) \uc124\uacc4 \ud728\uac15\ub3c4 \uc0b0\uc815\n   a = As x fy / (0.85 x fck x b) = 68.128 mm\n   \u00d8 Mn = \u00d8f x As x fy x (d - a / 2)\n        = 0.85 x 2026.8 x 400.0 x (520.0 - 68.128 / 2)\n        = 334864421.5 N.mm \u2500\u2500\u2500> O.K (Mu = 100000000.0 N.mm) [S.F = 3.349]\n\n\n10) \uc804\ub2e8\uac80\ud1a0\n  \u03a6 Vc = \u03a6v x \u221afck x b x d / 6\n     = 0.75 x \u221a35.0 x 400.0 x 520.0 / 6 = 153818.1 N\n  \u03a6 Vc \u2265 Vu = 50000.0 N  \u2234 \uc804\ub2e8\ubcf4\uac15 \ubd88\ud544\uc694\n\n\n===========================================================================\n                                \uc0ac\uc6a9\uc131(\uade0\uc5f4) \uac80\ud1a0                                 \n===========================================================================\n\n11) \uade0\uc5f4\uac80\ud1a0\n  \u2460 \uc751\ub825 \uc0b0\uc815\n    fs = M / [As x (d - \u03c7/3)] = 60000000.0 / [ 2026.800 x ( 520.000 - 162.89 / 3 )]\n       = 63.567 MPa\n    \u03c7 = -n x As / b + n x As / b x \u221a [ 1 + 2 x b x d / ( n x As ) ]\n      = -7.3 x 2026.8 / 400.0 + 7.3 x 2026.8 / 400.0 x \u221a [1 + 2 x 400.0 x 520.000 / (7.3 x 2026.8)]\n      = 162.894 mm\n    \uc0ac\uc6a9\ucca0\uadfc\ub7c9 = 2026.800 mm\u00b2  (\ucd5c\uc678\ub2e8 \ucca0\uadfc\ub3c4\uc2ec : 80.0 mm)\n      1\ub2e8 : D 25 - 4.0 EA, 2\ub2e8 : D 0 - 0 EA, 3\ub2e8 : D 0 - 0 EA )\n\n  \u2461 \ucca0\uadfc\uc758 \ucd5c\ub300 \uc911\uc2ec\uac04\uaca9\n    \uac15\uc7ac\uc758 \ubd80\uc2dd\uc5d0 \ub300\ud55c \ud658\uacbd\uc870\uac74\uc740 \u300e \ubcf4\ud1b5 \u300f \uc801\uc6a9\n    Cc = 80.0 - 25 / 2 = 67.50 mm\n    \uc5ec\uae30\uc11c Cc ; \uc778\uc7a5\ucca0\uadfc\uc774\ub098 \uae34\uc7a5\uc7ac\uc758 \ud45c\uba74\uacfc \ucf58\ud06c\ub9ac\ud2b8 \ud45c\uba74\uc0ac\uc774\uc758 \ub450\uaed8(mm)\n\n    Smin : 375 x (Kcr / fs) - 2.5 x Cc = 375 x (210 / 63.567) - 2.5 x 67.500 = 1070.099 mm\n           300 x (Kcr / fs) = 300 x (210 / 63.567) = 991.079 mm\n    \uc5ec\uae30\uc11c Kcr = 210 ( \ucca0\uadfc \uac04\uaca9\uc744 \ud1b5\ud55c \uade0\uc5f4 \uac80\uc99d\uc5d0\uc11c \ucca0\uadfc\uc758 \ub178\ucd9c \uc870\uac74\uc744 \uace0\ub824\ud55c \uacc4\uc218 )\n    \u2234 Sa\ub294 \uc791\uc740 \uac12\uc778 991.079 mm \ub97c \uc801\uc6a9\n    Sa = 991.079 mm  \u2265 suse = 98.333 mm  \u2234 O.K", "flexure": "===========================================================================\n                          \uac15\ub3c4\uc124\uacc4\ubc95(USD)\uc5d0 \uc758\ud55c \ud728\ubaa8\uba58\ud2b8 \uac80\ud1a0                           \n===========================================================================\n\n1) \ub2e8\uba74\uc81c\uc6d0 \ubc0f \uc124\uacc4\uac00\uc815\n   fck = 35.0 MPa, fy = 400.0 MPa, \u00d8f = 0.85, \u00d8v = 0.75, Es = 200000 MPa\n   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n   |  B(mm)   |  H(mm)   |  d(mm)   |  \ud53c\ubcf5(mm)  |   Mu(N.mm)   |   Vu(N)    |  Ms(N.mm)  |\n   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n   |   400    |   600    |  520.0   |   80.0   |  100000000   |   50000    |  600000